Camoflage::
She was in fox mode.  She was running over to the bushes where she 
heard a noise.  She ran over and started crouching as she slowly 
approched a clump of bushes.  She slowly moved the bushes out of the 
way and looked down and saw a wolf bot laying on the ground panting. 
She turned and yelled back to Blackfang. "HEY LOOK! I found a bot!"
